Teodoras Balčiauskis.

A young bass player from Šiauliai, Lithuania, plays in Elzė Urbietytė’s band. Has a solo project “Seodophy”. 3rd place winner in bass category of Lithuania’s national guitarist competition “Gitarų šelsmas 2019”.

Released a solo album “Daunted” in 2017, releasing a solo EP “The after hours” in 2019.
